{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"2":"Prayer (Kitab Al-Salat)"},"section_detail":{"2":{"hadithnumber_first":391,"hadithnumber_last":1160,"arabicnumber_first":391,"arabicnumber_last":1160}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":509,"arabicnumber":509,"text":"حدثنا حميد بن مسعدة، حدثنا اسماعيل، عن خالد الحذاء، عن ابي قلابة، عن انس، مثل حديث وهيب . قال اسماعيل فحدثت به، ايوب فقال الا الاقامة","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (607) Sahih Muslim (378)"}],"reference":{"book":2,"hadith":119}}]}